        class="text-[#064d9f] opacity-80 dark:text-white text-center text-1xl font-semibold flex justify-center flex-row md:text-2xl sm:text-2xl max-w-[700px] mt-16"
      >
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Ducimus nostrum
        veniam dolore quis placeat cupiditate sed minus tempora beatae quidem
        cumque incidunt blanditiis odio, consequatur eligendi porro quam
        repellat esse!
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
